sources.description:
Unexpected Romance at the Lakehouse | Mistletoe Magic | HD Hallmark Holiday Romance Movie - When a successful NYC businessman inherits his grandfather's Maine lakehouse, he learns that the will stipulates carrying on the family's festive Christmas legacy. He hires a local event planner, and gets more than he ever could have bargained for.

Watch Mistletoe Magic, a full Hallmark Christmas movie where a successful NYC businessman inherits his grandfather’s Maine lakehouse and discovers that the will requires him to continue the family’s festive Christmas traditions. Hiring a local event planner to help, he soon finds himself swept up in holiday magic—and unexpected romance. Perfect for fans of Hallmark Christmas movies, romantic holiday films, full free Hallmark Christmas movies, cozy winter romances, and heartwarming festive stories, Mistletoe Magic delivers love, laughter, and the true spirit of Christmas.
